Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:03.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Filling in the distance between hate and love...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.31,0:00:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deductions and the suspense of two people!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A difficult case in search of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A courtroom clash between Kisaki and the prosecution!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.24,0:00:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An onsen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't been to one in so long, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's fall leaf-viewing season now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:57.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I recommend this open-air bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say this onsen is really good for the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, you have to take a break from work once in a while and just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does my schedule look like for next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The current court case is scheduled to be resolved next week, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's left depends on what you decide as far as the issue of the duty roster...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you would bring the documents for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's a duty roster?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes there are defendants who cannot employ the services of a lawyer due to financial reasons and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when the government appoints an attorney, but when none of us wants the case, it's left to the duty roster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've only given the case a quick glance-over, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why no one chose to take it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the defendant has a decent case here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's because the opponent is unfavorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:00.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:04.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one heading this case is Prosecutor Kujou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Madonna of Prosecutors, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:18.92,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,COURTROOM CONFRONTATION II: KISAKI VS KUJOU\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we say we're occupied and refuse it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of a case is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's something that occurred about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body of a company's president was found in his office in Haido City.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the fingerprints and the articles left inside the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were able to apprehend the defendant—a habitual offender that had broken into many establishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't seem like a case that would end up in court...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the defendant had already admitted to breaking in, being discovered by the victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And against his better judgment, hitting the victim in the head with the ashtray during the struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he problem is with the charge listed on the indictment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:07.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the indictment, it is charged as a robbery-murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But in that case, wouldn't it be an accidental death?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:14.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I find it hard to imagine Prosecutor Kujou would have made such a mistake, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuriyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already have the prosecutorial and fact-falsehood memos, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:26.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still lack the conditional examination papers—could you get them for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll also need a copy of the autopsy report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to this, the onsen will have to wait for another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Tokyo Detention Center
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me confirm once more with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the night of the incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.18,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You broke the window to the Ootsu Real Estate Company's office on the second floor of the Nomoto Building...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:51.18,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Inoue Takashi (55)\NSuspect
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:52.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And proceeded to enter the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While you were searching around the office, and trying to open the safe in the company president's office...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were discovered by the company's president, Ootsu Toshiyuki, when he returned for business purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, during the struggle, you used the glass ashtray to strike him in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All this resulting in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is all correct, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to the money in the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, according to testimony from the company employees...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 12,000,000 yen in cash taken in that day from a real estate transaction had disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:38.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The prosecution believes that, after you killed President Ootsu, you opened the safe and stole the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't know anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's certainly true that the money wasn't found in your room, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given that your fingerprints were found on the dial of the safe, the prosecution's suspicions aren't entirely baseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really didn't take the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And about that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you know the victim beforehand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times did you strike the victim's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two times?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, I was surprised and discovered unexpectedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the autopsy, there are traces of the victim having been struck three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was the third that proved to be the fatal blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were a single time, it'd be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But with two or three times, the possibility exists that you would be regarded as having intended to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:47.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am your ally, so even if it's unfavorable towards your case, please tell me everything honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me confirm once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really didn't intend to kill the victim, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In court, we shall press that one point in our argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.94,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Tokyo District Court
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:08.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant Inoue Takashi, at approximately 20:30 hours on the night of the incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:11.95,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The Case of the Robbery-Murder of the Real Estate Company President\NFirst Public Hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the second floor of the Nomoto Building in Haido City Block 3-2-9...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Broke the window of the Ootsu Real Estate president's office and trespassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While searching for money and other goods...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was discovered by that company's president, Ootsu Toshiyuki, who had returned to attend to business matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using a weapon in his possession...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He threatened that same person to open the door of the safe in the room...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:36.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And utilizing a glass ashtray that was also in the room, struck the victim's head three times until he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then stole the 12,000,000 yen deposited in the safe, and escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we request that the defendant be charged under Article 240 of the Penal Code, Robbery-Murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And sentenced to life in prison with hard labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does the defendant admit to the prosecution's accusation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or do you deny it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only entered to steal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As far as intention to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Proceed, counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The accusation is robbery-murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the defendant did not intend to murder the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Therefore I would like to raise an objection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he denies the charge of robbery-murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe it would be more appropriate to change the charge from Article 240 to Article 205, Assault Leading to Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defense appears to have an objection with the prosecution's accusation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any concerns?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason the defendant chose Ootsu Real Estate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just that while I was looking for a building to enter and steal from...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I happened to come across that building by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just a coincidence that you chose to steal from Ootsu Real Estate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you contend you had no existing grudge whatsoever against the victim Ootsu Toshiyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is all of this correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Prosecutor Kujou is trying to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:08:59.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The prosecution's aim with this line of questioning is unclear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant is familiar with a female by the name of Endou Noriko, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no reason you would forget your only daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:24.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was only eight years old when he divorced his ex-wife twenty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wonder what that has to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it that you can't answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Objection!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The prosecution only seeks to put the defendant at unease by bringing up the name of a blood relative!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that daughter relevant to the court in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Endou Noriko runs a snack stand in another building that Ootsu Real Estate manages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has been rumored that she was involved with the victim, Ootsu Toshiyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying it was not by coincidence the defendant broke into the building that became the crime scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We also have testimony to the effect that the defendant held a grudge against the victim because of his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, shall we ask the person in question?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since she is in the visitor's gallery, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can have her come out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:25.14,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Endou Noriko (28)\NInoue Takashi's Daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noriko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is the card the Madonna had hidden up her sleeve?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's necessary, we are prepared to have Endou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} testify as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's true what the prosecutor said?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was deceived by that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said sweet things such as how he would allow me to keep the shop, and took terrible advantage of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did you get into contact with your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I reunited with him nearly two years ago when my mother passed away from illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since, he would occasionally stop by my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you told him about Ootsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:24.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he'd get consolation money out of him for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's certainly turned into an unfavorable situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, if he held a grudge against the other party and hit him as many as three times...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one would believe him even if he said he didn't intend to kill the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lastly, I'd like for you to answer me truthfully...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you also think your father murdered Ootsu Toshiyuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Daddy likes stealing, but he's not someone who would kill a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like the battle to come will be an intense one this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dozing off again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just resting my eyes while thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's dozing off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, have you hit upon it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A good idea you can use to help Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking on this sort of case, it's Eri's own fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant had a motive to murder, and on top of that his fingerprints were clearly on the dial of the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:47.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is somebody supposed to defend against that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wonder why the dial on the safe was the only place his fingerprints were found?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for that, he probably snuck in wearing gloves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:13:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, since gloves get in the way when it comes to precise tasks such as turning the dial on a safe, he removed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when the victim came in, and so using the ashtray...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, his fingerprints should also be on the ashtray since it was the weapon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he'd taken his gloves off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there were no fingerprints left on the ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, of course he wiped his fingerprints off afterward!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Read this part carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it written here that there are traces of it having been wiped down with an oil-stained cloth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:31.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's so, why didn't he wipe down the safe as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:37.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He accidentally killed someone, so in his haste, he fled and forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wonder when he stole the money from the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, after he committed the murder, he opened the safe again, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just say he fled in haste?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it seems mismatched, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Criminals do all kinds of things that don't make sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just a sophism?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:06.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dad, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:17.00,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,List of Articles Found at the Crime Scene\N1. Glass Ashtray\N2. 1 Pair of Army Cotton Gloves\N3. Eyeglasses screw\N4. Golf Ball
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, just something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You came to the scene of the crime to see if there was anything you could do to help Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Great Detective sure has a lot of free time, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, you came to investigate the crime scene as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting permission from the building manager right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:07.51,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Akiyama Takuya (56) Building Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.21,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.51,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister, you were the first person to discover the company president?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could we hear a detailed account of what happened at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On that night, at around 9:00, I was watching a baseball game on TV when...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Dad—no, I mean, Mr. President?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I made my rounds at 8:00, no one was in the office...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he left my restaurant a bit ago, he said he was coming back to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, he must've come in through one of the emergency exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the door to the office is locked, and there was no answer even though I called for him many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't he be in the rear office?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to drop off the reading glasses he left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could you come and open the door for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:08.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} you mentioned was President Ootsu's adopted son-in-law, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He runs a nearby Italian restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was this door that was locked, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:20.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used this spare key to open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure doesn't look like he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:36.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me, Masahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's someone there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone inside is being beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key for the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The company president is the only one with the key to this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:01.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move aside please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:10.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, please hurry and call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:13.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:24.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The company president's office is over there, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, this door is locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is in possession of the key to this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:40.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the attorney I mentioned on the phone and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Detective Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:46.75,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Arima Masahiko (35)\NProprietor of an Italian Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:45.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You're the famous...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:46.96,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:50.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, apologies for interrupting your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:53.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were wondering if you would let us take a look in the company president's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, is this room not being used right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though the police have already completed their investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:04.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it was the room in which Dad died under such circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say what we'll do with it from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just as the police left it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where was it that the victim fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was right around here, in front of the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was on the floor, cradling his head in his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That's how it was"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:47.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, Inoue was discovered by the victim as he was trying to open the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant had already stated as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's important is what happened afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inoue used a knife or something he had hidden on him to threaten the victim into opening the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, when it was opened, he used the ashtray, and from behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Struck him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not saying the defendant is lying, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:11.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if he wanted you believe that he was innocent, that's probably it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way to defend a defendant if you don't believe him, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can say all the neat phrases you want, but you're only going to get thrashed by that Madonna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say Mister, where you saw the culprit from...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it this tiny window?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:42.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogorou, could you stand in front of the safe again for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just wait there for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-le!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:06.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From here, Uncle is hidden by the screen and I can't see him at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I saw wasn't over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just the shadow of a person I saw reflected over on this wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A shadow reflected on the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, the lights in the room were off...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I saw the culprit's shadow reflected by the neon lights shining in from the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow of someone hitting Ootsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after that, I also heard the sound of Ootsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} falling to the ground, so there's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did not, then, see Defendant Inoue actually striking the victim, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Miss Attorney...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not an important difference, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit even said that he struck him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Merely seeing a shadow of someone striking another...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is completely different from seeing the actual person striking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:06.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter the circumstances, until the defendant is tried and a guilty verdict comes down in court...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is still considered a defendant, and not a culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When such sad feelings are involved, everyone tends to confuse the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:21.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This clock's stopped, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a prize that the late company president won in a golf tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:30.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was placed there as a commemoration ornament, and isn't usually used.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, if you could come over here a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:35.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The combination to the safe in question...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did anyone else know it outside the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, only my father knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For security reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't even tell the accounting heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:53.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're in the way, just loitering around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:22:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, I understand it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick behind this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow of someone beating someone else that Akiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} supposedly saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the sound of something having fallen...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using this trick, it could all be manufactured!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.89,0:22:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the one who set this trick up...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gould only be that person!
